<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>The Bachelor's Irena Srbinovska really is the whole package.</p>

<p>Not only is she beautiful, smart and caring, the blonde beauty is also an excellent cook.</p>

<p>In news that will no doubt be welcomed by Locklan 'Locky' Gilbert, Irena told The Huffington Post that she loves baking, and has won several cooking competitions in the past.</p>

<p>Irena wowed the judges at Tastes of Central Geelong comp back in 2013, with her 10-layered chocolate-coffee Opera cake, and took home the top prize.</p>

<p>She did it again a year later, this time at the Central Geelong Bake Off when she churned out an impressive 500 macaroons.</p>

<p>Following the victories, Irena almost opened her own local cafe.     </p>

